description.narrative: Thailand has made a significant progress in advancing ECD policy with a big milestone in endorsing the ECD Act with UNICEF contribution. The Act benefits pregnant mothers and families of children under 6 years old, with a strong emphasis from the government that multi-sectoral and integrated contributions are needed at national and local levels. UNICEF continues to leverage support and provide technical expertise required to advance overall ECD policy environment and encourage enabling policies that can support an integrated and inclusive ECD programme. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
